{
  "stem": "15938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we had lots and lots and lots of aunts and uncles and cousins, cousins who were older than my father.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there was a lot of generation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My generation was the third generation I was friendly with.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were my age because there was such a big age gap between the brothers and the sisters.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But these were living near us, and my father had another sister who was living in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she used to come every summer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And those-- there were four, two brothers and two sisters-- and they were the-- we were the closest together, even after the war there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's where I ended up with one of-- his two of the sisters together and-- and that's-- they remain to me the only relations-- one from-- the two sisters' children, they kind of looked after me when I came back from the camp.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1939 the Hungarians took over, took away the businesses, took away the property, and things got very bad.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were a little bit longer better off because, we thought, because my father fought in the first world war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he had a lot of metals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we thought that that-- we did benefit a little bit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not benefit, but we could keep the business a bit longer than the other Jews who-- and then they started-- My father went up to Budapest to try to get papers.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, try to do something to make it illegal for us to become part of this setup.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it didn't succeed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's-- after three months later they took our land away and then the business away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the beginning of the end-- the four years of hard struggle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, not as a child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
